      <title>随着中国经济低迷回归，亚洲股市暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市周一难以取得太大进展，原因是全球提前降息的可能性逐渐减弱，令市场情绪恶化，而中国市场假期结束后仅小幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 00:24:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
